fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">one of the most heartwarming and appealing of them all. &quot;—Leo and Bobbie </div><div class="t mcfa x74 h2d y18d1 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jane Van Dolson, </div><div class="t mb54 xa4 h4a y1662 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Boost Your Prophets, </div><div class="t m3c0 xae h2d y1662 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 14, 15. </div><div class="t md13 x60 h6c y1363 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What contrast does God draw between His great love for Israel and </div><div class="t m75a x74 h6c y1664 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their response to His love? Hosea 11:1-4. </div><div class="t mde x60 h2d y1760 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The </div><div class="t m400 x50 h4a y1344 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">New International Version </div><div class="t m368 x1f h2d y1344 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">translates verse 4 this way: &quot;I led them </div><div class="t ma29 x74 h2d y163e ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with the cords of human kindness, with ties of love; I lifted the yoke from </div><div class="t m255 x74 h2d y1b3f ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their neck and bent down to feed them.&quot; </div><div class="t m788 x14 h13 y229d ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">64 </div><div class="t m257 x92 hfe y1e84 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MON </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
